{"gold_evidence": ["doc_quartz#chunk_001", "doc_calcite#chunk_001"], "id": "minigeo_013", "question": "石英和方解石在矿物类别上有什么区别？", "result": {"abstained": false, "answer": "石英属于硅酸盐矿物，主要化学成分为二氧化硅（SiO2）；而方解石属于碳酸盐矿物，不属于硅酸盐矿物。", "citations": ["doc_quartz#chunk_001", "doc_calcite#chunk_001"], "confidence": 0.95, "evidence": [{"chunk_id": "doc_quartz#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_quartz", "license": "public", "mineral": "quartz", "page": null, "score": 53.58677613450202, "source": "MiniGeo curated mineral notes", "text": "石英是常见的硅酸盐矿物，主要化学成分是二氧化硅 SiO2。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/quartz"}, {"chunk_id": "doc_calcite#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_calcite", "license": "public", "mineral": "calcite", "page": null, "score": 50.69694194657993, "source": "MiniGeo curated mineral notes", "text": "方解石是典型碳酸盐矿物，不属于硅酸盐矿物。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/calcite"}, {"chunk_id": "doc_quartz#chunk_003", "doc_id": "doc_quartz", "license": "public", "mineral": "quartz", "page": null, "score": 42.40678970871775, "source": "MiniGeo curated mineral notes", "text": "石英硬度通常高于方解石，适合与碳酸盐矿物做性质对比。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/quartz-hardness"}, {"chunk_id": "doc_calcite#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_calcite", "license": "public", "mineral": "calcite", "page": null, "score": 36.45005850926642, "source": "MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes", "text": "方解石的碳酸根特征带常接近 1085 cm-1，可用于与石英区分。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/calcite-spectra"}, {"chunk_id": "doc_dolomite#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_dolomite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "dolomite", "page": null, "score": 36.41645655493346, "source": "MiniGeo curated mineral notes", "text": "白云石与方解石同属碳酸盐体系，但含有镁，反应和谱学解释需要区分。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/dolomite"}], "raw_model_output": "{\n  \"answer\": \"石英属于硅酸盐矿物，主要化学成分为二氧化硅（SiO2）；而方解石属于碳酸盐矿物，不属于硅酸盐矿物。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    \"[doc_quartz#chunk_001]\",\n    \"[doc_calcite#chunk_001]\"\n  ],\n  \"abstained\": false,\n  \"confidence\": 0.95\n}"}}
